Last "accidental" shooting I recall is one in Lousiana.  A guy and his girlfriend went over to a friend's house where he unloaded and showed them his .45 caliber Glock handgun.  When the friend went in the other room, the guy took the handgun, loaded it, worked the slide, aimed the gun at his girlfriend's head, and pulled the trigger.
<br />

<br />
